item.title: Cost of Your Caffeine and Sugar Fix to Stay High on El Niño
item.description: Cost of Coffee and Sugar to Stay High in 2023 The cost of coffee and sugar is expected to remain high in 2023 due to the El Niño climate pattern. El Niño is a climate pattern that causes warmer-than-normal ocean temperatures in the Pacific Ocean.
